The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 09 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guest is John Stossel, host of Fox Business' "Stossel" and author of "Myths, Lies & Downright Stupidity: Get Out the Shovel - Why Everything You Know Is Wrong," on whether Republicans can capitalize on America's strident anti-Washington sentiment, his plan to balance the budget in one fell swoop, and how John Stossel would "win the future".
